item.title: Gatsby Experiment
item.description: Hi, how did the day go?, what about the week? what about the month?, Good I hope!. Personal update: I almost bought a guitar, But then I realised something and stopped, the decision correct or wrong? the future holds the truth, hope you got the answer with you! future me reading this. Pew!… I almost did not post this month, although I completed the project/experiment in the middle of the month.
